---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import book_cover from "../assets/front-cover.png";
---

<Layout title="book">
  <main class="flex-column items-center justify-center">
    <h1 class="mt-10 text-center text-3xl text-gray-700">
      Decoding Startup Success Factors
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-center text-gray-700">a UC Berkeley Analysis of AI, Blockchain, and Healthcare Company Profiles</p>
    <div class="mx-auto mb-20 mt-10 w-80 shadow-sm">
      <Image src={book_cover} alt="Picture of the book" class="w-full" />
    </div>
    <div class="mx-[20%] text-center text-gray-700">
      <p>
        Why do some startups make it and others do not? 
        <em>Decoding Startup Success Factors: a UC Berkeley Analysis of AI, Blockchain, and Healthcare Company Profiles</em>, 
        is a book made up of multiple business profiles from startups in the AI, blockchain and Healthcare sectors 
        written by UC Berkeley students. It features some of the most relevant business profiles for the reader to 
        gain insights into specific companies. It also features data aggregated from many more profiles to give the reader insights 
        into the general success factors of startups in the different business areas. This book is valuable 
        to all entrepreneurs or aspiring entrepreneurs wanting to learn and gain insights into what separates that 
        companies the make it from the ones that do not. The book can be found on Amazon and can be purchased both 
        as a digital and a paperback version.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
